commit 0cb793c8b70ad1784215704c135068ee6a12bc33
Author: Brian Bidulock <bidulock@openss7.org>
Date:   Thu Nov 14 10:16:13 2013 -0700

    set full properties on selection and check windows

    These properties are now set on selection window, and
    in addition to other properties on the check window:

      - set WM_NAME
      - set WM_CLASS
      - set WM_COMMAND
      - set WM_CLIENT_MACHINE
      - set _NET_WM_PID
      - set _NET_WM_NAME

    Selection window properties are set before the MANAGER
    message is sent for selection WM_S%d.

 COMPLIANCE      | 12 +++++++-----
 src/Screen.cc   | 34 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 src/blackbox.cc |  3 ++-
 src/blackbox.hh |  6 +++++-
 src/main.cc     |  2 +-
 5 files changed, 48 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)

