commit e22911b8a55a53ff6fdbf748683e687b705ac7e2
Author: Brian Bidulock <bidulock@openss7.org>
Date:   Mon Sep 30 09:47:59 2013 -0600

    more EWMH support: all types, states and actions

    - trivial support for _NET_WM_STATE_STICKY (unused)
    - trivial support for _NET_WM_STATE_SKIP_TASKBAR (unused)
    - trivial support for _NET_WM_STATE_SKIP_PAGER (unused)
    - support for _NET_WM_STATE_DEMANDS_ATTENTION
    - support for _NET_WM_STATE_FOCUSED

    - trivial support for _NET_WM_ACTION_STICK

    - trivial support for _NET_DESKTOP_LAYOUT (unused)
    - trivial support for _NET_HANDLED_ICONS (unused)

