commit 6d58c1f1839dd9cf5d20479bbf5e4341167e1685
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:   Tue Oct 18 11:33:25 2005 +0000

    some small focus fixes... if someone sets focus to an override
    redirect window *without* grabbing the mouse, then we should react to
    the focus out even as if it was a normal focus out event (instead of
    ignoring it).

    this makes rdesktop sort of work in full-screen mode (since they do
    this kind of evil thing)...

