 lib/Rect.cc | 14 ++++++++++++++
 lib/Rect.hh |  2 ++
 2 files changed, 16 insertions(+)

commit 79cfa3ec98b52779ad0d4737f11b87b89f963f48
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:   Fri Mar 18 21:37:20 2005 +0000

    the "Focus Last Window on Workspace" feature should not keep "sticky"
    windows focused...  this is quite annoying when you switch to an empty
    workspace (with a single stick window) and then switch back to a
    workspace where a window previously had focus... before, blackbox
    would keep focus on the sticky window... now it focuses the window
    that previously had focus.

 src/Screen.cc | 7 +------
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 6 deletions(-)

