commit 5d69eeb9b48debb525be2c2b262133738238b9b8
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Jan 10 14:50:13 2005 +0000

    since transients are kept on the same workspace as their parents,
    there's no reason to check if a transient is on the same workspace
    when raising...

    as a side effect, when raising a group, all windows on all workspaces
    will be raised... i'm not sure if this is going to cause problems, but
    i suspect not... i am even considering keeping all windows in a group
    on the same workspace

