commit 3e7ddeece1429efa2d7897086bb305076b86c9b2
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Dec 21 08:49:37 2004 +0000

    reorder the workspace menu as suggested in tracker 700159:

	For a more ergonomic Workspaces menu: Have the 'Icons' member at
	the top of the list, nearest the mouse pointer when the menu is
	opened. Have the 'New Workspace' and 'Remove Last' members at the
	bottom of menu, as far away from the original mouse location as
	possible.

    this makes good sense...

