commit a6f8401d3ae61ad7244715d092c4a0460ff8d738
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Dec 20 14:49:17 2004 +0000

    1. transients are iconified/deiconified with their parents... make sure
    this works!

    2. split out BlackboxWindow::setState() into:

       setState(), which sets WM_STATE
       updateEWMHState(), which sets _NET_WM_STATE
       updateEWMHAllowedActions(), which sets _NET_WM_ALLOWED_ACTIONS

    note: setState() calls updateEWMHState() and
    updateEWMHAllowedActions() (i.e. no functional difference).  however,
    we use the updateEWMH*() functions instead of setState(current_state)
    in Window.cc

    3. don't put transients with a valid non-transient parent into the
    client/icon menus (see 1. above)

 src/Screen.cc	  | 16 +++++++++++++---
 src/Window.cc	  | 44 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------------
 src/Window.hh	  |  2 ++
 src/Workspace.cc | 12 +++++++++++-
 4 files changed, 58 insertions(+), 16 deletions(-)

