Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri Oct 1 15:55:35 2004 +0000

    when setting/clearing fullscreen and/or maximize, store the previous
    size in client coordinates, instead of in frame coordinates... this
    solves the problem where the frame geometry is wrong after clearing
    fullscreen and/or maximize after a style change

