commit a8e0f790209ab987a66a9eb1cd110ba7d9a74ace
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Aug 31 14:20:55 2004 +0000

    EWMH requires that strings be in UTF-8.  with this change, the
    bt::Netwm API requires Unicode strings (bt::ustring) and converts to
    UTF-8 automatically.  If the system cannot convert to UTF-8, then
    bt::Netwm does not set the related property

