commit 4bf9c0c30eb6632f9d5e3a0029eb937aa344bc47
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Aug 31 10:47:41 2004 +0000

    improve unicode support:

    1. change the bt::ustring type to basic_string<unsigned int> to avoid
    confusion with std::wstring

    2. fix UTF-8 <-> UTF-32 conversions

    3. fix iconv(3) code to use the correct data type sizes

    4. UTF-32 strings normally begin with a BOM (byte order mark) to allow
    the program to determine the endianness.  bt::ustring should not
    contain the BOM, and it should be converted to the native endian

 lib/Unicode.cc | 57 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------
 lib/Unicode.hh |  4 +++-
 2 files changed, 47 insertions(+), 14 deletions(-)

