commit a4b2217a3e47ac56d616c6de922518b5af844722
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Mar 2 11:09:12 2004 +0000

    fix a couple of bugs:

    1. don't use resource.numberOfWorkspaces() during runtime... add
    BScreen::workspaceCount() and use that instead (fixes a crash when
    trying to change to a newly created or newly removed workspace).

    2. when the user adds/removes workspaces via the workspaces menu,
    automatically save the resources so that they are preserved across
    restarts.

