commit ae74a8f7e727bbda39df626a041eef8286b6f664
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Feb 23 15:34:35 2004 +0000

    add Blackbox::XGrabServer() and ::XUngrabServer(), which implement a
    sort of ref-counted grab on the X server (since the Xlib functions
    don't do this).  this allows us to optimize things like restarts and
    workspace switching, so that we do only a single grab/ungrab (instead
    of one grab/ungrab per managed window).

 src/Screen.cc	 |  8 ++++++++
 src/Slit.cc	 |  9 ++++-----
