Date:	Thu Nov 27 16:14:45 2003 +0000

    install libbt.pc when installing libbt... this is a pkg-config file
    that will report the CFLAGS and LIBS necessary to compile and link a
    program against libbt.  it correctly lists Xft as a dependency if Xft
    support is enabled

    cleaned up configure.ac to use PKG_CHECK_MODULES instead of looking
    for xft-config explicitly.	recent Xft versions install an xft.pc
    file, so we simply let pkg-config do it's job :)

