commit 33bd00b600f024ee7988e3025690c3df05a592af
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Thu Oct 23 12:25:55 2003 +0000

    1. remove maximium width/height and use heap storage for all image
    processing (instead of stack storage)

    2. update the floyd-steinberg dither to be a bit simpler and easier to
    understand.  we now do a bi-directional sweep of the image, which is
    recommended by several papers covering the diffuse dither algorithm

