Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Sep 24 16:45:18 2003 +0000

    add support for full-screen windows as described in the EWMH.  this is
    done intelligiblely, and even preserves the maximized state (if any)
    when transitioning to/from full-screen mode.

    decoration toggling didn't really work that well, but should work a
    but better now (don't have a real test for this other than full-screen
    though).

    in general, some other cleanups happened to make the code a bit easier
    to manage.

