commit 585a9ed38fcde4759f57d63293b594c6afabe6a7
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Jun 23 06:41:41 2003 +0000

    font-related APIs now take a screen parameter

 src/BlackboxResource.cc |  2 +-
 src/Screen.cc		 |  3 ++-
 src/Toolbar.cc		 | 15 +++++++++------
 3 files changed, 12 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

commit 7634633472ad132f2717a8c5ff631f73f5c7985a
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Jun 23 06:40:10 2003 +0000

    add Xft support to libbt...

    since Xft cannot create fonts for use on all screens, we have to
    change the API slightly for font-related things to take an 'screen'
    parameter.

    all in all, this is rather straight forward... we use the UTF-8
    variants of the Xft API, but at the moment we have no real UTF-8
    support.  we need to get this before we release 0.70.0

 lib/Font.cc | 191 ++++++++++++++++++++++++-----
 lib/Font.hh |	17 ++-
 lib/Menu.cc |	 8 +-
 lib/Pen.cc  | 375 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------
 lib/Pen.hh  |	28 ++++-
 5 files changed, 496 insertions(+), 123 deletions(-)

commit 99dd8fa4d688c10bbec7fe8b6b638069b25bb125
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri Jun 20 10:11:19 2003 +0000

    new smart placement algroithm

    this uses a grid fit algorithm to find the best place for new
    windows... it scales (roughly) linearly in contrast to the old one
    which scales exponentially.

 src/Workspace.cc | 398 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--------------------
 1 file changed, 241 insertions(+), 157 deletions(-)

commit 829a58736c6170200ab11d5030c35f517a356e8f
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Thu Jun 19 07:41:40 2003 +0000

    improve the menu UI 'feel' by delaying menu hiding as well as
    showing... this allows the user to have a more pleasant experience
    when opening submenus even if they happen to move the mouse over other
    items in the menu 'on the way' to the submenu.

 lib/Menu.cc | 79 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------
 lib/Menu.hh |	3 ++-
 2 files changed, 63 insertions(+), 19 deletions(-)

