commit d77772fc7aab818bdb1c8c9505d512596a58f819
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Jun 18 12:50:39 2003 +0000

    get the link order right for libs with dependencies.

    -lXext depends on -lX11, so they chould be listed as '-lXext -lX11'
    and not '-lX11 -lXext'

