commit 3009f41f8fccf9dc3b75db072bc5d6c73a093ece
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Wed Apr 23 22:26:04 2003 +0000

    Blackbox no longer writes its config on exit / restart.  Instead the config
    is written whenever it is changed.	This means blackboxrc can now safely be
    edited while the wm is running.

