commit cfbe0e022d71d07d33d9e61752cb81129523cdcf
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Tue Mar 4 20:07:15 2003 +0000

    needed to change std::string to a char*, would not compile otherwise.

 lib/Application.cc | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

commit 436d8ba6e5e7fd9d11573ac2be4c6c4c32258433
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri Feb 28 16:52:53 2003 +0000

    update the way signals are handled and delivered to the application:

    the signal handler doesn't call a virtual function anymore, instead it
    remembers which signals have been delivered, and the eventloop calls
    bt::Application::process_signal(int) so that the app can handle the
    signal gracefully.

    the RunState stuff has been cleaned up.  some convenience functions
    wrap the bt::Application specific runState() and setRunState()
    functions.	The startup() and shutdown() virtual functions are called
    just before and just after the eventloop runs (respectively).

    blackbox proper has been updated to work with these new changes.

 lib/Application.cc | 193 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----------------------
 lib/Application.hh |  39 +++++++---
 src/Rootmenu.cc    |	2 +-
 src/Screen.cc	    |	5 +-
 src/Window.cc	    |  11 +--
 src/Workspace.cc   |	2 +-
 6 files changed, 142 insertions(+), 110 deletions(-)

