commit 721f1efe8865c813c9aec5511c2432faadb123d0
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Feb 17 08:41:53 2003 +0000

    rework the MITSHM support to not leave an attached image segment
    laying around.  create it when needed, and destroy it when done.  this
    prevents shared memory leaks if blackbox (or some other app using the
    lib) crashses.

 lib/Image.cc | 160 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------------------------
 1 file changed, 78 insertions(+), 82 deletions(-)

