commit a4d96e78cb9cb641778209a51a11b8a18c32cc3c
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Thu Feb 6 18:26:06 2003 +0000

    added a way to get resource.double_click_interval to screen class

    various touchups to the BlackboxWindow class.  Chief here is a restructure
    of the button press and release events.  The if .. else tree is based
    on the
    window the event occured on only.  This creates a more consistent UI.  xOr
    submitted a similar patch a few months back and this is based largely
    on his
    ideas.

