commit c58da3d0442f98e5c98bf7383a82e6f04fa19183
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Jan 8 09:05:52 2003 +0000

    remove ImageControl from API

    add bt::Menu::updatePixmaps() which is called just before the menu is
    shown.  use this function to make sure the pixmaps needed for this
    menu are rendered (through the pixmap cache).  when the menu is
    hidden, the pixmaps are released.  comment from the code:

    // release the pixmaps for this menu... menus are not visible 100% of
    // the time, so they should not use pixmap memory 100% of the time

 lib/Menu.cc | 91 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--------------------------
 lib/Menu.hh | 18 ++++--------
 2 files changed, 54 insertions(+), 55 deletions(-)

commit 080a3bd0045d2bc0c8cd31ec4dc2e1ed556be86f
