commit e7ade9a1d7e432ce15763fd28788f74115a527e3
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Jan 8 08:59:05 2003 +0000

    say goodbye to ImageControl, and hello to PixmapCache

    it doesn't make sense to have a bt::Pixmap object just to control pixmap
    caching.  instead, give control of this over to the programmer with a very
    simple and straightforward static bt::PixmapCache API

 lib/ImageControl.cc | 214 ------------------------------------
