    update blackbox to use the new bt::Image dithering modes.  this
    includes saving and loading the session.imageDither key.

    this resulted in a new config submenu - the dither menu.  the C
    translation has been updated to include the new strings needed in the
    new menu.

    i also removed the colors_per_channel resource from blackbox, since we
    can use the static bt::Image methods for the same purpose

