commit 3106f19c4f5912a8b753b832a7def79b637b0bc4
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Oct 30 17:15:26 2002 +0000

    big API revision...

    since Image is display/screen independent, Color and Texture should be
    as well.
    when we actually need an X resource from a color/texture/image, we use
    the appropriate member method, passing in the display and screen.

    one noticable difference is that Color does not have a string name anymore.
    instead, use Color::namedColor, which needs a display and screen to parse
    the colorname into rgb values.

    this ended up being a completely rewrite of Color, with has a new cache
    mechanism.	Texture didn't require as many changes (thankfully).

    a result of this required changing the GCCache and Pen interfaces, and
    adjusting all code accordingly.

    ImageControl is still alive, pending some decisions on its replacement.

    bsetroot has been updated to not require imagecontrol at all.

    unfortunately, this is a big update, since all code using Pen, Color, Image
    and Texture had to be adjusted to the new API.

 lib/Color.cc	     | 317 +++++++++++++++++++++++-----------------------
 lib/Color.hh	     | 107 +++++-----------
 lib/GCCache.cc      |	 8 +-
 lib/GCCache.hh      |	39 +++---
 lib/Image.cc	     |	66 +++++-----
 lib/Image.hh	     |	11 +-
 lib/ImageControl.cc |	24 +++-
 lib/Menu.cc	     | 128 ++++++++++---------
 lib/Texture.cc      | 148 +++++++---------------
 lib/Texture.hh      |	77 +++++------
 src/Screen.cc	     | 331 ++++++++++++++++++++----------------------------
 src/Slit.cc	     |	19 ++-
 src/Toolbar.cc      | 134 +++++++++++++++-----
 src/Window.cc	     | 149 +++++++++++++++++-----
 src/blackbox.cc     |	 5 +-
 util/bsetroot.cc    |	62 ++++-----
 util/bsetroot.hh    |	10 +-
 17 files changed, 817 insertions(+), 818 deletions(-)

