commit a2b845ec10ee992701a12dccb8d1ee0b7ef42a0c
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Oct 30 08:13:12 2002 +0000

    reduce bt::Image to nothing more than width/height and rgb data.

    this means that a particular image is not tied to any given display/screen,
    and
    can be rendered to a pixmap multiple times on many different screens (!)

 lib/Image.cc | 143 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------------------
