commit 2fbefe3e6bcdf18e72647c47e9d3e7294e405352
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Oct 29 13:05:59 2002 +0000

    set a hardcoded maximum image size (4000x3000).  use this in all the
    places where we build gradient tables on the stack.

    massive cleanups to the gradient functions to make them a bit more
    readable, use more correct C++, and hopefully perform a bit better
    (profiling tests pending).

