 2 files changed, 361 insertions(+), 526 deletions(-)

commit e1f1bfa6e31e94f4f6e3606754b5ee62859a1df7
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Oct 29 09:15:25 2002 +0000

    step one of the assassination of ImageControl.

    get rid of the sqrt tables and gradient buffers.  these really aren't
    needed,
    and since the gradient buffers used such a small area, we can use the stack
    instead.

