Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Tue Oct 15 15:23:32 2002 +0000

    removed the reinterpret cast thanks to Marius Nita's comments, after
    reading the Stroustrup tome it seems reinterpret cast is for things like
    int -> pointer not pointer -> pointer.

 lib/Netwm.cc | 58 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------------------------
