commit 5c2255c894a01a141d9ea8a19786badc7d3ca39c
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue Oct 15 12:43:33 2002 +0000

    as discussed with shaleh:

    when focus has nowhere to go, put it on the root window (PointerRoot morexi
    specifically).  this way we don't rely on the toolbar's window to be always
    visible, and we can allow the toolbar to not be created if the user is
    using a EWMH compliant dock (KDE/GNOME/etc.).

