commit cf88c3d0a790db22f3dbef3ed2b2bcec6573fd9a
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Oct 14 15:08:27 2002 +0000

    the new Menu code.

    this is a complete rewrite of the menus used in blackbox, based on the code
    from moving_target (but done much cleaner).

    everything works, except for tearing off menus (which will require more
    research to get working properly in both the window manager and clients)

    since the menu Menus are real popup menus, the Application class needs
    to have
    extra code for delivering events in 'popup mode'  this is also complete and
    working.

    nothing uses the new menus yet, since they will require some changes to the
    style format to work totally and correctly

