commit 3d41b6cb3c7c5a11b6bcb7c30cdee472dbd6bdce
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Wed Oct 9 16:29:16 2002 +0000

    add support for borders to bt::Texture

    bt::Image understands these when rendering, and adjusts bevels accordingly

    Bevel2 has been obsoleted, the same effect can be acheived by using
    a border
    width of 1 and the texture and border colors being the same.

