Date:	Mon Sep 30 20:52:20 2002 +0000

    menu elliding for long menu entries.  Had to add this because of apps which
    create insanely long titles (like ksirc).  It ensures the text is never
    longer than 60 chars and eats the middle of the string to accomplish this.

