commit d6396357bcf9e78085cfce03b3c683787ed0928c
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri Sep 20 16:54:38 2002 +0000

    add new EventHandler mechanism: a generic event delivery mechanism.

    remove the old save*Search mechanisms the Blackbox class.  Blackbox still
    needs a window list for doing focusing changes.  I hope to have a better
    solution for this soon.

    move most of the generic event deliver compression/delivery code to
    BaseDisplay, but keep window manager specific event handling in Blackbox.

 lib/BaseDisplay.cc  | 196 ++++++++++++++++++++-
 lib/BaseDisplay.hh  |	31 +++-
 lib/EventHandler.hh |	84 +++++++++
