commit f070690d235fb8461640216d8dd3a7fb07573ebd
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri Sep 20 16:49:15 2002 +0000

    restore window gravity properly.  when restoring an ICCCM compliant
    client window, the window is never moved to the new position before
    the client can perform the reparent, resulting in the client window
    being in the wrong place.  this fixes this.

 src/Window.cc | 13 ++++++++++---
 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

