commit d400a6b96e8244872f16ef7e1522e53be168622a
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri Sep 20 16:11:04 2002 +0000

    revise netwm api:

    the functions are now consistent in the sense that the first argument
    is the
    window on which to store the property, followed by the data to set.  Also,
    since we create the Netwm object with a display pointer, i have changed it
    to store this pointer, and removed the Display * from all the functions.

