commit ac5c6b40de102ecfca1f538bcde21c1b0e5f2ba2
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Fri Aug 2 07:51:02 2002 +0000

    added a enter and leave notify handler for BlackboxWindow.	This event
    takes
    over control of the colormap that was done in the process_event() loop
    previously.  It also takes over control of auto raise.

    Blackbox used to have some code borrowed from twm to implement an event
    queue scanner which tried to locate LeaveNotifies in order to help avoid
    useless processing.  Since it was only used for EnterNotify I simply
    implemented it as a loop in the function.  Smaller, more concise code is
    usually a good thing.

 src/Window.cc	 | 45 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 src/Window.hh	 |  2 ++
 src/blackbox.cc | 42 ++++++------------------------------------
 3 files changed, 47 insertions(+), 42 deletions(-)

