commit 03c784c1f9015aada46858aa93f290f04fa19e19
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Thu Jul 25 22:10:00 2002 +0000

    moved slit handling into Screen::manageWindow() where it belongs

    if remaximize() is called while the window is shaded, ensure the attributes
    are still set.  This was the cause of the shade + maximize weirdness.

    client.initial_state was cruft from before the reordering of the
    constructor,
    it is gone now.

    minor style touchups

