commit 2b9e75370f908289b52d54016f13a12d80c27a8b
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Wed Jul 3 17:36:42 2002 +0000

    *) from woodblock via xOr we have a couple of unitialized variable cleanups

    *) beat shaded, iconified windows with a bigger stick (-:  when blackbox
    exits
       or restarts shaded windows are marked as being in Normal, not Iconic
       state.
       The window constructor and restoreAttributes() check if the window's
       state
       was Iconic and if not removes the iconic state.	This way an iconified,
       shaded window comes back iconified and shaded and a window shaded comes
       back in NormalState.
       Note restoreAttributes() marks the window 'WithdrawnState' this is the
       marker for a window waiting to be placed on a Workspace and is only
       temporary, a few lines later it is placed and the state correctly set.

    *) fix a bug in transient handling where the transient is closed and
    tries to
       give focus to its parent, even if the window is iconified or on
       a different
       Workspace.  Updated the assert in setInputFocus to reflect that
       we believe
       no call chain will get here if the window is not on the current
       workspace

    *) propertyNotifyEvent now takes an event as its argument just like all
    of the
       other event handlers

    *) added prints on the entry to each event handler, wrapped in DEBUG
    of course

 src/Screen.cc	  |  2 ++
 src/Window.cc	  | 67 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--------------
 src/Window.hh	  |  2 +-
 src/Workspace.cc |  9 +++++--
 src/blackbox.cc  | 10 +++-----
 5 files changed, 62 insertions(+), 28 deletions(-)

