commit 57707cbb0accf95dfed0d8686c66bb13d643e71c
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Mon Jul 1 04:51:11 2002 +0000

    client.rect was != to reality on initial startup of the wm, turns out
    configure() was getting called but nothing was happening because it was
    configuring with the already set values.  Replaced the call to configure
    with a simple client.rect.SetCoords().  BlackboxWindow::show() now has an
    assert to test this when DEBUG is enabled.

    Added xOr's patch (with tweaking) to cleanup the menu show code on
    buttonPress.

 src/Window.cc | 90 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------------------------
 1 file changed, 45 insertions(+), 45 deletions(-)

