commit 13de527f1aafab3184edeef6ab5884b408e532ec
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Wed Jun 19 21:01:36 2002 +0000

    solved the assert being triggered on workspace change.  A window that
    was not
    on the current workspace was getting a focus event because of a race
    condition.
    If the workspace changing happened too rapidly the focus events would be
    delayed.  This resulted in a window trying to get focus much later than was
    intended.  The solution it turns out was quite simple: ignore focus
    events if
    the window can not accept them.  Some small cleanups are also in this
    patch.

 ChangeLog	  |  6 +++---
 src/Screen.cc	  | 15 ++++++++++-----
 src/Window.cc	  | 11 ++++++++++-
 src/Workspace.cc | 33 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 src/blackbox.hh  |  2 +-
 5 files changed, 51 insertions(+), 16 deletions(-)

