commit ffc6cc744c3423c20ab9b8bf7634ba4e66e30378
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Thu Jun 6 04:01:12 2002 +0000

    BlackboxWindow::remaximize() refuses to work if the window is shaded

    BlackboxWindow::shade() calls remaximize() when reverting the window if the
    window was maximized before shading.  This both fixes the problem
    with strut
    changes unshading windows it also means that when combined with the above
    change we do not compute new maximizations unnecessarily.

 src/Window.cc | 33 +++++++++++++++++++--------------
 1 file changed, 19 insertions(+), 14 deletions(-)

