commit d5380a9194aa652eef0f6c1acb1164e0854812a8
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Thu May 30 20:57:11 2002 +0000

    Fixed snapping code so it only snaps once if full max is enabled

    for maximized windows the edge snap code broke because it depended on
    less than
    checks and for a maximized window the edge distances are always equal.  The
    code now uses less than or equal for left and top giving them a slight
    bias.

 src/Window.cc | 52 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++-------------------------
 1 file changed, 27 insertions(+), 25 deletions(-)

