commit 7aff6ede4d095a1ee1996b8f4d2f37c0fa897c10
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Fri May 24 08:28:25 2002 +0000

    when moving *AND* resizing the window, we should tell the X server to do it
    all at once with XMoveResizeWindow (in ::positionWindow()).  this fixes
    a funny effect when demaximizing, where the full size window is moved into
    place, and resized afterwards.

