commit 9b80646842a53c0a4f43ab1a9dd720b79f1f2670
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Tue May 21 12:42:59 2002 +0000

    rewrite transient handling/stacking to allow a window to have multiple
    transients (not just one like it has been for years and years).

    i tested this fairly thoroughly (with a window that had mulitple
    transients,
    and each of those transients had multiple transients).  it now needs wider
    spread testing to find bugs i missed.

