commit a60a2b9d5ea23499b97ca22ea025c8342e98ee81
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Sat May 18 05:31:48 2002 +0000

    fixed windows that use resize increments.  window->constrain() did not
    take base_width/height into account when factoring the size so (((x /=
    inc) * inc) + base) could be greater than the constraint.

