commit 663a84f2ae520df68a07098f06ab6eb099c32413
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Thu May 16 22:25:27 2002 +0000

    the handling of decor toggling was broken due to the items not being
    mapped.  The old code would unmap the windows to disable them.  This meant
    that called XMapSubwindows() was harmful.  The new code actually removes
    the decor element so when it is brought back it must be mapped

 src/Window.cc | 27 ++++++++++++++++++++-------
 1 file changed, 20 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

