commit 2839bda50aee2ecaf9bc83f6f3de13b76503c1cf
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Thu May 16 17:16:03 2002 +0000

    convert toolbar to rect

 src/Toolbar.cc | 127 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----------------------
 src/Toolbar.hh |  16 ++++---
 2 files changed, 80 insertions(+), 63 deletions(-)

commit 094b27b2982a758117bd668cb69a8dffb769ace3
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Thu May 16 16:10:09 2002 +0000

    convert more parts of BlackboxWindow over to Rects... i also removed the
    y_border and y_handle stuff, and added a margin strut.  this makes it
    10 times
    easier to calculate the frame rect from the client rect (and the other
    way),
    which makes the maximize/resize/upsize/downsize/positionWindows/etc. all
    much simpler.

    I also changed frame.rect to hold the total size of the window (the
    full width
    of the window including the border around the window). updated the smart
    placement code to use this instead.  the framerect is also changed when
    shading a window, so there is no need to check for this in the smart
    placement
    code.

    all in all, things are very good... window menu placement needs some work,
    which i will do this weekend

    OH, this change was prompted by my finding an off by one error while
    resizing
    windows.  resize an xclock to 200x200, and it really gets the size
    of 201x201.
    this has also been fixed now.

 src/Window.cc	  | 557 +++++++++++++++++++++++----------------------------
 src/Window.hh	  |  20 +-
 src/Workspace.cc |  12 +-
 3 files changed, 268 insertions(+), 321 deletions(-)

