commit 29efe041392da24c5ebb28510881857ab5c5b66f
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Wed May 8 22:45:39 2002 +0000

    Lots of small cleanups and refactors:

    BaseDisplay now stores a run state rather than use a startup and
    shutdown bool

    number_of_screens was redundant

    most menus stored a screen variable which was redundant as the Basemenu
    they
    are all derived from has a getScreen() method.  Why store two Screen*'s per
    instance?

    various const, static, and formatting cleanups

    began converting BlackboxWindow to the texture->render() method more
    work to
    follow here

