commit 0442a96fcd29d4441d52a07d044e279c767d4b34
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Sat Apr 20 17:02:26 2002 +0000

    mapNotify was working on already mapped windows, this was causing the last
    window on the workspace to get focus even when 'last focus window' was set.
    It also meant windows were getting two or three setInputFocus() calls.
    setInputFocus() now checks if the window is focused before continuing.

