commit fc9244ac38b9e2613a1579b11fa021041d35eab6
Author: bradleyhughes <bradleyhughes>
Date:	Mon Mar 25 09:11:02 2002 +0000

    temporary fix for:

    * use bbkeys to open a window and then close it via bbkeys.  If it is
    the only
      window left open, blackbox will spin in a screen->unmanageWindow loop and
      then die.  Tons of X BadWindow messages will appear as well. (nyz)

    this needs to be fixed better, and the focusing code in blackbox needs
    to be
    much more robust...

