commit b35188d86ee8f4c301a904dd708db1ddc7cfcfe9
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Sat Mar 23 21:58:47 2002 +0000

    unmanageWindow now takes a boolean parameter which indicates whether
    the client should be remapped after being restored.  unmap and destroy
    set this to False, reparent and shutdown set this to True.

