commit 9823041904c8dd435b3c44a195b0065637dc93a2
Author: shaleh <shaleh>
Date:	Fri Mar 15 22:53:00 2002 +0000

    Big changes, small changes.  Mostly clean ups.  One or two bugs.

    BaseDisplay gave a lot of its functionality to Blackbox.
    Basemenu now uses find() whenever it needs to find a member, other assorted
    menu cleanups.
    screen->toggleFocus() added.  The goal was to prevent a system wide
    reconfigure
    for a simple change in focus model.
    moved bexec to Util, all emx functionality is now in Util
    basename is now in Util as well

    general: unsigned and const cleanups, more work to be done here.
	     most blackbox classes can not be copied, made this more clear by
	       placing the copy constructor and op= in private sections
	     all functions in headers now give argument names as well as type
	     a few more uses of string over char*, more work here too

    this adds one HUGE bug though -- changing Styles leaves the style menu open
    and any attempt to close it kills blackbox with a sig11.

